   CRAWFORD-ARTS _ ATLANTA _ Feature on the great partnership
bewtween patron Virginia Carroll Crawford and cuator Donald Peirce,
who together built one of High Museum of Art's most important
collectons: American decorative arts. A show featuring the
collection opens june 12 at the High. (Fox, Atlanta
Journal-Constitution). 25. WITH COLOR PHOTOS. FOR SUNDAY
</P>
<P>
   DAVIDKELLEY-Q&AMP;A _ Interview with David E. Kelley, creator of
