   The Fort Worth Star-Telegram plans to move the following stories
for clients of the NYTimes News Service for AMs of Saturday, June
12, and thereafter. If you have any questions, please call Tom
Uhler, Paul Wagner or Jim Peipert on the Star-Telegram's
National/Foreign Desk at (817) 390-7785. &QL; 
