<P>
   NEW YORK _ The last time Lauren Green played piano on national
television was in the 1985 Miss America pageant, when she had so
little time to change between performances that she took the stage
missing a key garment. That likely won't happen this week as the TV
anchor competes in the Cliburn-sponsored amateur piano competition
in Fort Worth. By LIZ STEVENS. Story has moved in ``e''
entertainment category. &QL; 
 &QL; 
