   FORT WORTH, Texas _ Michael Hawley, one of the competitors at
this week's Cliburn International Piano Competition for Oustanding
Amateurs, is one of several bona fide geniuses in the field. But
he's probably the only one who's worked for ``Star Wars'' creator
George Lucas. By WAYNE LEE GAY. Story will move in ``e''
entertainment category. &QL; 
