<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-06-11 18:06 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A2218 &Cx1f; taf-z
s f &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-INVEST-COLUMN-ART-$AD     06-11 0693
