   BASEBALL
</P>
<P>
   BBN-LONGBALL _ ATLANTA _ You'll have to pardon John Smoltz if he
spends a lot of time needling Greg Maddux and Tom Glavine about
who's the best hitting pitcher on the Braves team. Maddux and
Glavine have the ``chicks dig the long ball'' commercial; Smoltz is
hitting better than .400 and coming off a 3-run home run on Monday
night. So we open the debate with the three _ Who's the best? _
then stand back and enjoy. (Wilkinson, Atlanta
Journal-Constitution). 20-plus.
</P>
<P>
   BBN-ROCKER-PROFILE _ ATLANTA _ Profile on the growth of John
Rocker, Braves relief pitcher from Macon, who has emerged with a 98
mph fastball, as one of baseball's top closers. (Rogers, Atlanta
Journal-Constitution). 30. WITH PHOTOS. MOVED.
</P>
<P>
   BBN-BRAVES-ORIOLES _ ATLANTA _ Braves vs. Orioles game story.
7:40 p.m. (Rogers, Atlanta Journal-Constitution). 13.
</P>
<P>
   BBN-BRAVES-NOTES _ ATLANTA _ Braves notebook. (Rogers, Atlanta
Journal-Constitution). 15.
</P>
