<P>
   COXNET NASCAR PAGE
</P>
<P>
   EDS: This is the CoxNet NASCAR page for the week. The layout is
now available.
</P>
<P>
   COXNET NASCAR 0612: GIBBS ON A ROLL _ Tony Stewart and Bobby
Labonte have made Joe Gibbs Racing one of the hottest teams in
NASCAR. (Levine, Atlanta Journal-Constitution) Art includes
4-column photo of Joe Gibbs, 18-pica color photo of Bobbyt Labonte
and 1-column color photo of Tony Stewart.
</P>
