<SLUG> BC-WORM12-COX </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    System administrators battle Explorer worm
 &HT;    (Eds: Moving in national (a) and financial (f) categories.
 &HT;    By Mark Clothier
 &HT;    c. 1999 Cox News Service
